   <uof name="Task_specification">
     <description>
	     The Task_specification UoF enables the specification of tasks and task methods. 
	     	<note>The method to be followed may be specified
			as a sequence of stages, including advisory stages, as repeating and conditional stages.
			A task may invoke another task as a stage.
		</note>
		A task may be related to states that it requires or generates.
